{"tid":1536324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國民教育借屍還魂] 聖心要學「我愛中國」","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:03:53.000Z","uid":257728,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"19873afc793970daa60b1e397f929771907f33be","tid":1536324,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"朋友個小朋友幼稚園開學<br />\n派新書見到要學<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「我愛中國」</strong></span></span><br />\n即刻嚇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ky5L5bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fky5L5bd.jpg&h=530cf253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救救香港下一代<br />\n堅決反對國民教育<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>借屍還魂</strong></span></span><br />\n你班局長又話唔好搞啲學生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇嘉諾撒聖心校友可以幫家長出聲<br />\n其他幼稚園咩情況<br />\n睇怕佢係中國國慶前就會教<br />\n諗起啲小朋友要學埋唱中國國歌就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日聖心，明日全港</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aeb698e83413fb8141b4d1ddbf087b5d51327b","tid":1536324,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"6ad15c71810f5e0c76c8ba8cb20e8c032c345e16","tid":1536324,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src